02:13 PM Defendant in court, in custody with Attorney Adam Matthias Welch.  Robin W Lee appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  All parties by Zoom. The defendant received a copy of the Complaint and waived reading. Defense moved to dismiss Count 1, made argument. Objection by State. Court denied motion. Court entered Not Guilty pleas as to any misdemeanor counts. Defense raised issue of competency. Court proceeded to bail pursuant to Local Court Rule.  The Court has reviewed the Complaint, makes a finding of probable cause and  ORDERS A COMPETENCY EVALUATION  pursuant to Wis. Stats. 971.14.  The Dept of Health & Family Services shall examine the defendant's mental competency to proceed. THIS COMPETENCY EVALUATION IS TO TRACK WITH OTHER OPEN CASES.  Competency hearing scheduled for April 14, 2022 at 11:00 am.
